FBIS3-27413 "drchi037_a_94002" FBIS-CHI-94-037 Document Type:Daily Report 24 February INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Foreign Ministry Holds Weekly News Briefing Liu Huaqiu To Visit South America OW2402084694 Beijing XINHUA in English 0827 GMT 24 Feb 94 OW2402084694 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, December 24 (XINHUA) -- Vice-Foreign Minister Liu Huaqiu will, as special envoy of the Chinese Government, attend the inauguration ceremony of President Frel of the Republic of Chile on March 11, at the invitation of the Chilean Government. Around this time, he will pay a working visit to the Republic of Venezuela and the Republic of Argentina upon the invitation of the foreign ministries of the two countries, a Foreign Ministry spokesman announced here this afternoon.
